==English==
===Pronunciation===
*[[IPA]]: /ˈæ.kju.ˌpʌŋk.ʧɝ/
*Other 1: (ăʹkūpŭngkʺchûr)
*Other 2: A-kyoo-punk-churr
===Noun===
'''acupuncture'''
# Pricking with a needle; a needle prick.
# The insertion of needles into the living tissues for remedial purposes.

